fc: class Solution { public:          vector<vector<int>> construct2DArray(vector<int>& a, int m, int n) {              vector<vector<int>> res;                  int siz = a.size();         vector<int> temp;                  if(siz != m * n)                                        return res;                  for(int i=0; i<siz; i += n) {                          for(int k=i; k<i+n; k++)                            temp.push_back(a[k]);                          res.push_back(temp);             temp.clear();         }                  return res;     }      };
